Distribution:
Sula Islands (Pulau Mangole); Peleng Island (Buko District, btw. Tantendeng village & Eben village, 
400–550 m
); 
Central Sulawesi
, Prov. 
Sulawesi Selatan
(Tana Toraja: Rantepao 
700–800 m
); Talaud Islands (Karakelang Island: Lobo).
